{"type":"answer","id":172811,"parentType":"question","parentId":18938,"uid":25766,"contents":"小震別怕，都不震才要擔心之後能量釋出太巨大<br>\n台灣之前才說前幾個月地震太少要擔心，還好最近有適當在釋放的感覺(?<br>\n<br>\n剛才發現中國震度的定義跟台灣不太一樣，所以做了個比較<br>\n感覺如果不是傳統土房的話中國5級地震(相當於台灣4級)似乎也沒到非常嚴重的地步，如果真的擔心就準備個地震包吧(<a href=\"https://www.fubon.com/insurance/blog/lifestyle/refuge-bag.html\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.fubon.com/insurance/blog/lifestyle/refuge-bag.html</a>)<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/b9fPrc3.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/b9fPrc3.png\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/b9fPrc3.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a>","date":"2020-02-21","agreeCount":0,"discussionCount":0}